Ramhorn:



Ramhorn walked into the bridge of the Ark, letting out a soft whimper.  

"AH SLAG IT!" he screamed, looking around the room.  Every computer console 
was destroyed and in pieces!  Most of it was charred from extensive flames.  
Meaning some idiot had let the things be on fire until the flames went out by 
themselves.

"Oh, no..." Ramhorn ran, hoping he was wrong.  

Ramhorn entered an orange room, a few screens with rocks through them and 
spike-shaped rocks sticking out of the 'cieling'.  A price you payed for 
crashing into a volcano.  He looked to Teletran-1 and Teletran-2.

"D--d---destroyed...I don't believe it." walking over to where the computers 
were supposed to be...he found none.  Just blown apart equipment sticking out 
of the metal wall. 

The rhino/Maximal fell to his skid plate, putting his head in his laps, 
shaking.
